[thinking] **Exploring POM formatter**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m considering testing the POM formatter. It seems the public SortPom might require artifacts, and I need to think about how to manage generic indentation, toggling on and off, and replacing literals. I should avoid duplicating the generic replaceRegex. There’s also a new feature that could let toggling off and on disable formatting in marked regions. I’m thinking I might use generic format alongside TrimTrailingWhitespace and TogglOffOn, potentially covered by a new class. I plan to inspect APIs using javap.
[thinking] 
