[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Exploring POM formatter**\n\nI’m considering testing the POM formatter. It seems the public SortPom might require artifacts, and I need to think about how to manage generic indentation, toggling on and off, and replacing literals. I should avoid duplicating the generic replaceRegex. There’s also a new feature that could let toggling off and on disable formatting in marked regions. I’m thinking I might use generic format alongside TrimTrailingWhitespace and TogglOffOn, potentially covered by a new class. I plan to inspect APIs using javap.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_033b21b2b7e854a7016a286d002a2881958130cfbae9991a46\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqKG0DZdJrBJ9TRTOcfsTdk0CKE4iKBMk3dlUO5OeNU4TindQFlAsKBsEpQMF_leFPPh2bMmszV5HAIfuMqXsKu8dMxLcFOtKKdbjqMsdMixrWtPY04rR42e0PpSD85uNdmjv1EwF77L0w1LqYYgAKhr-99ulWuQgFj0wuaVI7B7ZpqqRN7hvFTLdsYDuVMClImz3S-68TpfrVJlsWO33t5Jc57rwtnsA_h3flLwDkZVbDgveGclDiQDUF_1zLjc_fG2f0kn7Ea_xkg2rV2gbrJGDhCZII_aO2dY0MWswOxJ-l_7KDyf4Htmj_CcxhKZdNJl15sLiavMAJbybsfyVXSnWfSYfS8J92jdXYqKORskZgq2T7E_kZ4AzuNT574H8LdHfKhD4LaJ-G1g9IXu_TznF14NtyfV8EyqYXGvGsatfCat1j2hVBfe8rYS4ENWBvFV3c6XILasqLmV-hIadH2F9hD42Sp6JD6rJtjmAL2zxz68kJIBP4MQi-wdIWrdwsmMC3-W3fJRg__jNXgtwvz6KxMp5z7duXB4BdYmU-mOug7IwfcdQrIhllwoICNxFE9yb0l_FplQG_bzLhhCWDP-F1mYVmxFNjBgeTEVHwjtfpIQFb6dpGMHQ4s0tcGu8t0YoWxWYD2NJgSNXmC6uiLe_z2XhAbyagXXMqZk_1thoJ6FLKp-Gf52UNKC6x-3UmO_6pGghZ7vAEX8hbttbqurCpazQx0zge8QW2aUBod9TIAugCE7HseRAghCuuOGDzrXi9d_MtZs8wNGlqevT4tPgkIYvKpOJxU8off4LCLojVRin-KKDZuyn7zYs3i3OVb24RQ6jiUUbfbKvtnH-WF5dHmA4FHG2ejvikS9LJKkE4663udOyqeu9sC_LN5YMJJ_qR9slxp_liA00nbJAd-aD1NnRHQvV9SKhHfkP18MwQfj3gqvN_rIFaAEgUttNIzxnEVO2fxQ-02ylyNE2l9gNsnsKE9cLUpuOmee28-QpObHkCPA5sn2J1UygpWnD_QnYFx5MtkcXJhmiq6GT3vGZroJiz0YO0Z-Yi7K2e7mjdtd0ghvKz_hZ0ZslYt2VuB5WmnUvEJLPaF_GWg5WZIgMtHq3azXxl6nSE4JRjW16nHGF9vI2Y1pCVG-gXKbqeiHBORJPpgIwcEIsQ-Zhy4bgW_qHC3q1T4K